{"tid":2431562,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"/bin/sh: node: command not found","createTime":"2021-03-03T17:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T06:56:09.000Z","uid":42296,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6fae22f399b5eab6de7b74b92a3f39171959c2","tid":2431562,"uid":42296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"啱啱想用 VSC 用做下D react project 黎練習下。 但係佢就 彈左 /bin/sh: node: command not found 呢一句出黎。 咁我就上 GOOGLE SEARCH啦，搵到呢個網址 <a href=\"https://tutswiki.com/how-to-fix-sudo-node-command-not-found-error/。我就\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftutswiki.com%2Fhow-to-fix-sudo-node-command-not-found-error%2F%E3%80%82%E6%88%91%E5%B0%B1&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=7f2e5f20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tutswiki.com/how-to-fix-sudo-node-command-not-found-error/。我就</a> <br />\ncopy 左呢一句出黎  <br />\necho 'export PATH=$HOME/local/bin:$PATH' &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc<br />\n. ~/.bashrc<br />\nmkdir ~/local &amp;&amp; ~/node-latest-install &amp;&amp; ~/node-latest-install<br />\ncurl <a href=\"https://nodejs.org/dist/node-latest.tar.gz\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnodejs.org%2Fdist%2Fnode-latest.tar.gz&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=d79c967e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nodejs.org/dist/node-latest.tar.gz</a> | tar xz --strip-components=1<br />\n./configure --prefix=~/local &amp;&amp; make install<br />\ncurl <a href=\"https://npmjs.org/install.sh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnpmjs.org%2Finstall.sh&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=19d65ee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://npmjs.org/install.sh</a> | sh<br />\nrm -rf ~/node-latest-install<br />\n<br />\n打係 terminal到。而家過左 20分鐘 個terminal 都味行完。我是唔是中左伏呢？"},{"pid":"9082d7b09fd529782f03606875834a7f47be40c6","tid":2431562,"uid":42296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T17:50:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tutswiki.com/how-to-fix-sudo-node-command-not-found-error/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftutswiki.com%2Fhow-to-fix-sudo-node-command-not-found-error%2F&d=UjOWczzRfTNgHoC3e3JiXyrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=3a51ae7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tutswiki.com/how-to-fix-sudo-node-command-not-found-error/</a>"},{"pid":"d40299bcddad52d105dfc44afd103fb71f26e6be","tid":2431562,"uid":23094,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T17:55:05.000Z","msg":"開個新Terminal再Run嚟睇吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e1eef54e62d7c19159e87cf282519a84eaa4e0","tid":2431562,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"似係要安裝 nodejs<br />\n點解唔先用 apt, yum 呢 D 安裝左先？"},{"pid":"d6e1c8e41764daac42ae1019834f9ac32ef0904b","tid":2431562,"uid":42296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40e1eef54e62d7c19159e87cf282519a84eaa4e0","tid":2431562,"uid":55597,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T17:56:22.000Z","msg":"似係要安裝 nodejs<br />\n點解唔先用 apt, yum 呢 D 安裝左先？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T18:08:19.000Z","msg":"TRY TRY 先"},{"pid":"737691509d0fd32cd32b7f8530490c073fcfc263","tid":2431562,"uid":70606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T18:31:36.000Z","msg":"安裝左node,試下reboot部電腦應該就得"},{"pid":"41457a5486fb3db224f102dcbe393ade49e4a7f4","tid":2431562,"uid":42296,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T19:07:41.000Z","msg":"有時覺得學programming 果陣 搞設備都搞到幾煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5ee5f07842375981f10f05f9bfa488e8a94920","tid":2431562,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T03:04:22.000Z","msg":"官網有binary package, 點解要